CONTEXT KleenePlusNonEndoCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT KleenePlusNonEndoCheck
{+ Test that Kleene plus fails on non-endomorphic relations.
   This verifies the type checker correctly rejects t+[A*C] when source and target differ. +}

RELATION t[A*C]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testKleenePlusFail: result = t+

ENDCONTEXT
